hopobject.body: Could you please repeat that? femigra donde comprar en chile Most of the posters need to get over their emotions and focus on the concepts of corporate governance. This article is spot on. Mr. Zuckerberg should not have taken the company public if he is not willing to abide by basic standards of corporate governance. To be listed on an exchange requires a company, no matter how “cool” or “visionary”, to abide by rules and norms that ultimately benefit society.
